{"tid":1254184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登以外一樣要吹雞，只得連登仔會越嚟越少人","createTime":"2019-06-24T03:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:25:11.000Z","uid":39752,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ca0ca4a5c4982f5a299445e52551319bfa3fb1","tid":1254184,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"612人多係因為好多打工仔請假出嚟<br />\n同埋連登以外有好多網媒同傳統媒體助攻（例如食錯藥嘅鳩假期）<br />\n一無咗呢啲幫手，就會得返連登仔<br />\n之後出嚟嘅人就會越嚟越少<br />\n<br />\n以後行動宣傳要最少預網媒同紙媒有時間做嘢<br />\n主動報料俾記者，有記者肯長期跟更佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">趕極要做到 day 1 中午吹雞，day 2 全日有媒體曝光，day 3 出嚟</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">至於非文宣連登仔，記得share去比較中立或偏自己人嘅朋友圈子，唔好覺得佢哋一定睇咗就唔貼<br />\n因為重覆曝光先會顯得件事重要，令到啲本來十五十六嘅人一齊出嚟</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe8067d7ee4a83805435ef7d66c8428c3a572f8","tid":1254184,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067b93f393ed79aaf41bde9739508f2ad86a105d","tid":1254184,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"8463c3c00187c7cdcea30739033c5f8d3e51edeb","tid":1254184,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690b03342ac7b249742487ead0f76932cecaf50b","tid":1254184,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea27f3cd9c4dfe0ca59d6d38c5492c54406c72e","tid":1254184,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim